            "text": "Q. Did God create man thus wicked and perverse?\n\nA. No; but God created man good, and after his own image—that is, in righteousness and true holiness; that he might rightly know God his Creator, heartily love him, and live with him in eternal blessedness, to praise and glorify him.",
