            "title": "Q. 12",
            "text": "Q. Since, then, by the righteous judgment of God we deserve temporal and eternal punishment, what is required that we may escape this punishment and be again received into favor?\n\nA. God wills that his justice be satisfied; therefore must we make full satisfaction to the same, either by ourselves or by another.",
