            "number": 14,
            "roman": "14",
            "title": "Q. 14",
            "text": "Q. Can any mere creature make satisfaction for us?\n\nA. None; for, first, God will not punish, in any other creature, that of which man has made himself guilty; and, further, no mere creature can sustain the burden of God's eternal wrath against sin, and redeem others therefrom.",
            "proofs": []
